<p>This module requires Perl &#62;= 5.005, Parse::RecDescent, File::Temp and OLE::Storage_Lite:</p>

<pre class="sh_perl">    <a href="http://search.cpan.org/search?dist=Parse-RecDescent/" class="podlinkurl"
